getExtentions

public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.Collection<Extention>>> getExtentions()
Description copied from interface: IPlugin
Returns all Extentions of the Plugin.

The Extentions are organized as a Map of Maps of Collections. The key of the first Map is the serviceid and the key of the second Map is the hotspotid.
